Running the Project
Backend

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Start the server:

uvicorn app:app --reload
Frontend

Navigate to the frontend directory and install dependencies:

npm install

Start the development server:

npm run dev

The dashboard will be available at:

http://localhost:5173
